         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">15/2/93 ¶  ¶ It was a great pleasure for me, highly esteemed Professor, to receive the new part of the  ¶ Acta ¶  in which you have thrown such full light on a large number of algae and especially Aus...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">93.02.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">15/2/93</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es war mir eine grosse Freude, hochgeehrter Herr Professor, den neuen Theil der "Acta" zu erhalten, in welchem sie auf eine Menge Algen und namentlich Austral. Arten solch volles Licht geworfen haben. Es ist mir auch sehr lieb, zu sehen, dass meine eignen Sendungen auch wieder neues Material geliefert haben, und gütig von Ihnen vor die öffentlichkeit gekommen sind! Das </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">hilft</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">, namentlich in diesen hier bedrängten Zeiten, mein Department aufrecht zu erhalten!!</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich kann Ihnen eine wahrscheinlich wichtige Sammlung von Algen aus der Encounter-Bay in Aussicht stellen, die von einer Dame (aber nicht meine alte Freundin Miss Cole) gesammelt sind. Diese collection ist mir versprochen, aber noch nicht angekommen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sollte, wie es wahrscheinlich ist, Herr Graf Wachtmeister Sie besuchen, so bitte ich Sie, ihn aufzufordern, mir seine künftige Adresse mitzutheilen, damit ich den höchst angenehmen Brief-Wechsel mit ihm fortsetzen kann.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Sie ehrend, der Ihre,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Ich mache indes wieder Anstrengungen, Früchte von <name key="Sondera">Sondera</name> zu erhalten, auch neue Beiträge aus der Champion-Bay.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">15/2/93</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was a great pleasure for me, highly esteemed Professor, to receive the new part of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Acta</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="">Agardh (1892).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> in which you have thrown such full light on a large number of algae and especially Australian species. I am also very glad to see that my own consignments also have produced new material again and have kindly been made public by you!<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Several entries state 'misit F. de Mueller' [F. von Mueller sent it] after the name of the collectors.</p>
               </note> That <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">helps</hi>
               </seg> especially in these desperate times here to maintain my department!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I can hold out a prospect to you of a probably important collection of algae from Encounter Bay,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>SA.</p>
               </note> which are collected by a lady (but not my old friend Miss Cole).<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'Miss Cole' not identified. The new collector was Jessie Hussey; see M to J. Agardh, 7 June 1893.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If, as is probable, Count Wachtmeister should visit you, I ask you to ask him to communicate his future address to me so that I can continue my very agreeable exchange of correspondence with him.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Meanwhile I am making efforts again to get fruits of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Sondera">Sondera</name>
               </seg>, also new contributions from Champion Bay.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>WA.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Sondera">Sondera</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
